parameters.name: AcrRegistryInfo
parameters.description:
The access credential configurations of the Container Registry Enterprise Edition instance.

>  If you use a Container Registry Personal Edition instance, you do not need to configure this parameter. If you use a Container Registry Enterprise Edition instance, you must configure this parameter.

parameters.name: Arn
parameters.description: The details about the ARN that is required for authorization.

parameters.name: ContainerGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the container group.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the instance.
